What you need to know:  Leading in the boys’ categories, Kevin Anyien starred in the15-18 year-old boys category after shooting a score of 80 gross, followed closely by Ryan Mutinda who took the runners-up position after carding a score of 84Nakuru’s Peter Gathogo’s gross score of 83 was enough to earn him bragging rights among 12-year-olds, followed by Aidan Gachora who shot 88 grossNCBA Bank Yaya Center Branch Manager Peter Omolo said that the tournament is important in developing the young golfers skills